  "description": "In a few days, Michael will be arriving, which means today feels like the right day to start tidying up the house: procrastinated enough that there\u0026rsquo;s a sense of pressure, and enough that things won\u0026rsquo;t have time to get messed up before his arrival!\nI think Terran mentioned last night that today is when he leaves for his train ride here - something he\u0026rsquo;s never done, and I\u0026rsquo;m excited for him! I\u0026rsquo;ve never done a legit long train ride in the US, despite some riding on cars around Appalachia, and my experience about train riding in Europe is out-dated, so I\u0026rsquo;m curious to hear what it\u0026rsquo;s like! I\u0026rsquo;m assuming it\u0026rsquo;s Amtrak he\u0026rsquo;s using, but I don\u0026rsquo;t know!\n",
